      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i've been looking at how certain tech giants and hedge funds seem to be calling the shots lately. like, everywhere you look, a new law passes that perfectly aligns with what these specific billionaire groups want, even when the public is totally against it. it almost feels like the elected officials are just actors reading a script written by a shadow cabinet of corporate elites. do you see these kinds of patterns in current political power structures? like, is there actually a group behind the scenes making these decisions?",
